getMaxPairs

protected int getMaxPairs(java.lang.Integer chainNum)
Get the maximum number of pairs to write to a file during the 'chainNum' phase.

Intended for extenders to override. Default is 10,000,000.

Where chainNum is

  • null or 0 for map phase
  • N > 0 for Nth reduce phase

getNumDigits

protected int getNumDigits(java.lang.Integer chainNum)
Get the number of digits necessary for rolling output files during the 'chainNum' phase.

Intended for extenders to override. Default is 3.

Where chainNum is

  • null or 0 for map phase
  • N > 0 for Nth reduce phase
